00:40:21,830 --> 00:40:23,370
祝贺你  总统女士
Congratulations, Madam President.

539
00:40:23,460 --> 00:40:24,790
谢谢你
Thank you.

540
00:40:28,380 --> 00:40:30,260
感谢大家再次信任我
Thank you all for once again entrusting me

541
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:32,930
从事此项高层行政工作
with this high office of civil service.

542
00:40:33,010 --> 00:40:35,720
今天对我们来说是一个新的开始
Today is a new beginning for all of us.

543
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:40,140
我们同担共同的命运
We share a unique destiny,

544
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:44,440
我们要创造自己的未来 但我们也不该遗忘过去
but our future is ours to shape and our past cannot be forgotten.

545
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:47,940
新的一天需要新的想法
A new day requires new thinking.

546
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:52,440
同时我想值此机会
And while I had intended on using this occasion

547
00:40:52,530 --> 00:40:56,870
