I have decided instead that a different gesture is called for on this,

550
00:41:06,460 --> 00:41:10,710
在我新任期的头一天 以总统的名义
the first day of my next term as your president.

551
00:41:10,800 --> 00:41:13,670
我们都需要正义
We all feel the need for justice,

552
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:17,140
我们都想要报仇
and we all feel the need for vengeance,

553
00:41:17,220 --> 00:41:20,970
